dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[Created to be used in Forest County 911 system for address location]
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This point data layer represents roads for Forest County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Forest_Roads_2017.gdb.[Road centerlines for Forest County 911 and GIS System]
dataIdInfo.idCredit: Forest County Register of Deeds [Created by North Central Wisconsin Regional Planning Commission]
dataIdInfo.suppInfo: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
